
@startuml
title Sample Sequence Flow Diagram

actor User
participant "Client App" as Client
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "Business Service" as Service
database DB

User -> Client: Perform action
Client -> API: HTTP Request
API -> Service: Validate & forward request
Service -> DB: Query / Update data
DB --> Service: Result
Service --> API: Business response
API --> Client: HTTP Response
Client --> User: Show result

@enduml